    about_label:"Who We Are",about_h2_1:"Two paths.",about_h2_em:"One vision.",
    about_p1:"We're Tobias and Julia. A Swiss nurse and a teacher of ancient wisdom who met on the road, found each other in ceremony, and at some point decided to stop travelling and start building.",
