    pill4_title:"Teaching",pill4_text:"Workshops and residencies for people who want to learn by doing, not by watching.",
    nepal_label:"Pokhara · Nepal",nepal_h2_1:"Monastery",nepal_h2_em:"Partnership",
    nepal_desc:"We have a deep partnership with the Pema Dechenling Monastery in Pokhara, Nepal — a living Buddhist monastery where ancient practice meets modern healing. Together we're building projects for Nepal and the world.",
    nc1_who:"Monastery",nc1_name:"Ayurvedic Medicine",
