    nc2_who:"Monastery",nc2_name:"Yoga Training",
    nc2_desc:"Yoga teacher training and immersive retreats at the monastery. Classical Hatha and meditation in an authentic setting — monks chanting at dawn, the Himalayas as your backdrop.",
    nc3_who:"Monastery",nc3_name:"Sound Healing",
    nc3_desc:"Singing bowl courses, sound baths, and vibrational healing. The monastery's resonance carries centuries of practice — learn from masters who live this tradition daily.",
    nc4_who:"Together",nc4_name:"Nepal Projects",
    nc4_desc:"Children's education, women's empowerment, and community support. Our partnership extends beyond wellness — we're building infrastructure for lasting change in the Pokhara region.",
